name: Oof That Was Hard
description:
Wow I felt very slow from the beginning. Kylee cut my hair today so maybe I’m Samson? Probably just because it’s SO HOT. 
Had to pause under a tree for 5 mins
Will be ending all my runs the rest of the summer at the lake
